	abstract = {Agricultural management influences the rainfall-runoff processes and has relevant effect on soil erosion, especially on hillslope vineyards. Mechanization in the inter-row is particularly important in this issues. Vegetation cover, soil structure modification and crust formation dramatically influence the overland flow.},
